                        <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1907">Anonymi 1907</persName> is commemorated in
                        <title ref="http://syriaca.org/work/254">The Himyarite Martyrs (text)</title>, a work
                        surviving in at least 11 manuscripts including <bibl type="syriaca:Manuscript" xml:id="witness1">variantes du ms
